data.description: Welcome to this inviting 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home nestled on a spacious corner lot located in the Elley Crossings subdivision. This charming residence offers an abundance of natural light, a functional layout, and a peaceful atmosphere. With its well-appointed bedrooms, bathrooms, and thoughtfully designed living spaces, this property provides the perfect setting for comfortable living and entertaining. Outside, the corner lot offers ample space for outdoor activities and entertainment .Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful home yours!
